  "title": "Gasar Hikayata ta Mata Zalla ta BBC Hausa 2023",
  "description": "<h2>Abubuwan da ake bukata:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Gajeren kagaggen labari (wanda bai gaza kalmomi 1,000 ba sannan bai wuce 1,500)</li>\n<li>Takaitacce tarihinki da kuma takaitaccen bayani kan labarin naki</li>\n<li>Bayanan da za a tuntube ki</li>\n<li>Ki karanta&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/hausa/articles/crgl32j2pg7o\" target=\"_blank\">Ka'idojin gasar</a>&nbsp;da&nbsp;<a title=\"Dokokin bayanan sirri na BBC\" href=\"https://www.bbc.com/hausa/articles/cz4pz9z0rn1o\" target=\"_blank\">Dokokin bayanan sirri na BBC</a>&nbsp;kafin ki shiga gasar</li>\n<li>Dole ne shekarunki ka da su gaza 18 sannan ka da su wuce 35, ya zuwa ranar da za a rufe gasar ranar 20<strong>&nbsp;ga watan Agusta 2023</strong>.&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Wannan gasa ce ga mata kawai.</li>\n</ul>",
